    %% External flows
    Client -->|"HTTPS/443 or HTTP/80<br/>TLS (configurable)<br/>No Auth"| IstioGW
    Client -->|"HTTPS/443<br/>edge TLS<br/>No Auth"| OCPRoute

    %% Ingress to service mesh
    AuthorinoSvc -->|"TokenReview +<br/>SubjectAccessReview"| K8sAPI
    IstioGW -->|"HTTP/8080 or gRPC/9090<br/>mTLS ISTIO_MUTUAL<br/>Authorized"| RestProxy
    OCPRoute -->|"HTTP/8080<br/>plaintext<br/>No Auth"| RestProxy

    %% Service mesh to external
    GrpcServer -->|"PostgreSQL/5432<br/>Configurable SSL<br/>Username/Password"| PostgreSQL
    GrpcServer -->|"MySQL/3306<br/>Configurable SSL<br/>Username/Password"| MySQL
    Operator -->|"HTTPS/443<br/>TLS<br/>SA Token"| K8sAPI
